== Third-party dependencies ==

This project depends on:
  - cryptography (Apache-2.0 / BSD): Ed25519 keypair generation, signing, and
    verification for the aep:0.7/signed profile.

The Node.js verifier in verifiers/node/ uses only the Node.js standard library
(crypto, fs, path) with no third-party dependencies.

== References ==

The AEP design draws upon and is compatible with the following open standards:
  - RFC 8259 (JSON)
  - RFC 8785 (JSON Canonicalization Scheme)
  - RFC 7515 (JSON Web Signature) — adapted for SIGNED_DIGEST
  - W3C JSON-LD 1.1
  - W3C Verifiable Credentials Data Integrity 1.0
  - BagIt File Packaging Format (RFC 8493) — DERIVED projection
  - RO-Crate 1.1 — DERIVED projection
